<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Confirmed</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #10b981;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2563eb;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .success-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #d1fae5;
      color: #065f46;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .invoice-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #1f2937;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .payment-details {
      background-color: #f0fdf4;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d1fae5;
    }
    .detail-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .detail-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #065f46;
    }
    .detail-value {
      color: #1f2937;
      text-align: right;
    }
    .amount-paid {
      background-color: #eff6ff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .amount-label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .amount-value {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #10b981;
    }
    .transaction-hash {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      word-break: break-all;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .checkmark {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      background-color: #10b981;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 32px;
      color: white;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">Movo</div>
      <div class="checkmark">✓</div>
      <div class="success-badge">Payment Confirmed</div>
    </div>

    <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
    
    <p>Thank you! Your payment has been successfully processed and confirmed on the blockchain.</p>

    <div class="invoice-title">Invoice #{{invoiceNo}}</div>

    <div class="payment-details">
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Product/Service:</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{productName}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Payment Date:</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{paidAt}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Amount:</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{amount}} {{currency}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Paid in USDC:</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{usdcAmount}} USDC</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="amount-paid">
      <div class="amount-label">Total Paid</div>
      <div class="amount-value">{{amount}} {{currency}}</div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
      <p style="font-weight: 600; color: #1f2937; margin-bottom: 5px;">Transaction Hash:</p>
      <div class="transaction-hash">{{transactionHash}}</div>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 5px;">
        You can verify this transaction on the blockchain explorer.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #92400e;">
        <strong>✓ Settlement Complete:</strong> Your payment has been converted and settled to {{merchantName}}'s account in local currency.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p>If you have any questions about this payment, please contact {{merchantName}} or reply to this email.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you for using Movo Payment Platform</p>
      <p>Secure crypto payments made simple</p>
      <p>&copy; {{year}} Movo. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

